data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bathroom all brick home that is only three years old. This home comes with a charming covered front porch and a covered 12'x12' back porch with a mounted fan. Inside you'll find luxury vinyl plank tiles and ceiling fans throughout the entire home. Vaulted ceiling in the living room with recessed LED lighting offers plenty of room to entertain your family and friends. In the kitchen you will find all stainless steel appliances, a deep stainless farmers sink, and gorgeous granite counters.  Upgraded solid wood cabinets topped with crown molding plus a large pantry give plenty of storage space. Both bathrooms have granite counters with quality vanities. Master bathroom has a double vanity and an oversized garden tub. The home offers a popular split floor plan with the master bedroom on the left side of the home and the guest rooms on the right side. There is a large 12'x24' shed behind the home that has a roll-up door and a metal roof. All windows come with a fabric shield storm protection system for your ease of mind. A high-efficiency Carrier HVAC keeps the home cool in the summer. The home sits on a large lot that backs to a wooded area. Nice and quiet setting outside of town but convenient to downtown Milton makes this an ideal location. This home will not last! Schedule your showing today!
